			<div class="block">
				
				<a name="imagelogo"></a>
				<div class="post-title">
					<h2>Logos and images</h2>
					<p>&nbsp;</p>
				</div>
				
					<p>Here are some images you can use for either print or screen. If you want to add <a href="#htmllogo">our html/css logo</a> to your site, we've made it easy (well, ish) for you.</p>

					<h3>Block logo, single line</h3>
					<p><a href="/img/logos/block-logo-1-line.png"><img src="/img/logos/block-logo-1-line.png" width="500"/></a></p>
					<h3>Block logo, triple line</h3>
					<p><a href="/img/logos/block-logo-3-line.png"><img src="/img/logos/block-logo-3-line.png" /></a></p>
					<h3>Pixel logo, green background</h3>
					<p><a href="/img/logos/LDF-logo.gif"><img src="/img/logos/LDF-logo.gif" /></a> </p>
					<h3>3D logo, monochrome</h3>
